_sText:
My second fast paced, low tier cave map all the while taking up 66,060,665 less bytes on your hard drive! That's a lot of bytes.

Playing with HDR on is recommended for the best experience, and at least medium textures is highly recommended to get the grid underneath the ramp glass.

It is designed with "sv_maxvelocity 4000" in mind, but will not hinder your progress if it's set at default 3500.

TF2 port courtesy of ShadowSheep, download here: https://www.resurfed.com/viewtopic.php?f=10&t=2152

CSGO port courtesy of Bro, download here: https://gamebanana.com/maps/206634
